# Phase 7 — cursor blink verification.
# Type "hi", capture at frame 2 (just typed, cursor visible),
# then wait for blink animation frames. Frame ~15 should be
# well into the hidden phase (past 500ms hold + 150ms fade).
0 key h
1 key i
2 capture /tmp/os-phase7-visible.png
15 capture /tmp/os-phase7-hidden.png
15 exit
